<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="The_Theory_of_Biological_Evolution">The Theory of Biological Evolution</span></h2>
<ul><li> <a href="//www.gutenberg.org/ebooks/" class="extiw" title="ebook:">On the Origin of Species By Means of Natural Selection, or, the Preservation of Favoured Races in the Struggle for Life</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/File:BookIcon.png" class="image"><img alt="BookIcon.png" src="//www.gutenberg.org/w/images/9/92/BookIcon.png" width="16" height="16" /></a> by <i><a href="//www.gutenberg.org/authors/Darwin,_Charles" class="extiw" title="author:Darwin, Charles">Charles Darwin</a></i>.<br />This work is not racist in itself, but has been used as base for many racist theories.</li></ul>
